    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>为什么是区间 DP？</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "因为每次操作只能取走最左边或最右边的元素，这意味着无论游戏进行到哪一步，<strong>剩下的元素始终是原数组中的一个连续子区间</strong>。因此，我们可以用区间的左右端点 $[i, j]$ 来表示游戏的状态。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>状态定义：</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "定义 <code>dp[i][j]</code> 表示当剩下的数组区间为 <code>[i, j]</code> 时，到游戏结束时，能够产生的 $(X - Y)$ 的值。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>如何如何判断当前是谁的回合？</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "初始数组长度为 $N$，当前区间长度为 $len = j - i + 1$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "那么已经被取走的元素个数就是 <code>used = n - len</code>。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "因为太郎先手，两人轮流取：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "当 <code>used</code> 为偶数时，说明现在是<strong>太郎</strong> 的回合。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "当 <code>used</code> 为奇数时，说明现在是<strong>次郎</strong> 的回合。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>状态转移方程：</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "1. <strong>太郎的回合 (<code>used % 2 == 0</code>)</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "他可以选择取走左端的 $a_i$ 或右端的 $a_j$。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "太郎要最大化差值，所以：<code>dp[i][j] = max(dp[i+1][j] + a[i], dp[i][j-1] + a[j])</code>",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "2. <strong>次郎的回合 (<code>used % 2 != 0</code>)</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "他同样可以选择 $a_i$ 或 $a_j$。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "次郎要最小化差值，所以：<code>dp[i][j] = min(dp[i+1][j] - a[i], dp[i][j-1] - a[j])</code>",
          "depth": 3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "ll dp[3005][3005];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tvar a = vector<ll>(n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> a[i];\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tint used = n - 1;\n\t\tif (used % 2 == 0)dp[i][i] = a[i];\n\t\telse dp[i][i] = -a[i];\n\t}\n\tfa(len, 2, n) {\n\t\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\t\tint j = i + len - 1;\n\t\t\tif (j > n)break;\n\t\t\tint used = n - len;\n\t\t\tif (used % 2 == 0) \n\t\t\t\tdp[i][j] = max(dp[i][j - 1] + a[j], dp[i + 1][j] + a[i]);\n\t\t\telse \n\t\t\t\tdp[i][j] = min(dp[i][j - 1] - a[j], dp[i + 1][j] - a[i]);\n\t\t\t\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout << dp[1][n] << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
